version_description:
Thanks for using the Green Flag App!
We have made some styling and journey enhancements to the App as well as adding an update prompt to ensure you are always using the latest version.
Architectural platform migration - to ensure you don’t get any interruption in service, please make sure you install this update.
The 'Rate my Driving' feature is back! Put your driving skills to the test. Drive 1000 miles and if you get a high enough score there could be some benefits for you at the end of it.

Thanks for using the Green Flag app.
In response to your feedback, we’ve changed the way you link your policy in the app.  If you’ve had issues in the past, please try again.

Thanks for using the Green Flag app.
In this update we’ve done some work to improve the experience for customers including fixing bugs and having a bit of a respray.
Fixes a bug which was logging users out in the background
We have improved the way we diagnose your vehicle faults in the Rescue Me Journey and fixed some bugs in the background
In this update we have added some behind the scenes enhancements to app
Fixes a bug that causes some push notifications to close down the app.

Thank you for using Green Flag.
This update provides more information about any pets in the car when you need a rescue.
Thanks for using the Green Flag app. This update provides minor improvements to Rescue Me.
Thanks for using the Green Flag app – the quickest and easiest way to get help if you break down. In this update, we’ve made some minor changes to optimise the app for new and current users.
Thanks for using the Green Flag app. We’ve added some minor behind-the-scenes updates to improve your experience with the app.

Well, we've been pretty busy. We’ve made it easier to navigate through the app, it’s simpler than ever to get in touch with us if you ever need support, we’ve made some tech improvements behind the scenes, and even squashed a few minor bugs. You’ll love it.
We’ve made it possible for you to access the brand new Green Flag Shop through the app.
We've made a few small changes to make sure the app runs as smoothly as ever on iOS 13.
We’ve made a couple of small changes that make it even easier for you to get in touch with us.

We've squashed a few pesky bugs and made some small improvements behind the scenes.
In our latest update, we’ve made some minor changes to the ‘Rescue Me’ journey.
